Excuse me!

1284
01:11:41,391 --> 01:11:42,475
Whoo! Yeah!

1285
01:11:44,102 --> 01:11:45,103
4-Town!

1286
01:11:48,940 --> 01:11:49,941
- Mei!
- Mei!

1287
01:11:50,066 --> 01:11:51,735
- You're here!
- What are you doing here?

1288
01:11:53,111 --> 01:11:54,529
I couldn't do it.

1289
01:11:54,696 --> 01:11:58,199
The panda's a part of me,
and you guys are too.

1290
01:11:58,742 --> 01:12:00,952
Mei, you threw us
under the bus.

1291
01:12:01,161 --> 01:12:02,996
I know and I'm sorry.

1292
01:12:03,163 --> 01:12:04,331
I've been, like, obsessed

1293
01:12:04,414 --> 01:12:06,082
with my mom's approval
my whole life.

1294
01:12:06,249 --> 01:12:08,585
I couldn't take losing it,

1295
01:12:09,711 --> 01:12:12,047
but losing you guys
feels even worse.

1296
01:12:12,964 --> 01:12:14,257
Well, too bad.

1297
01:12:14,924 --> 01:12:16,259
'Cause you did.

1298
01:12:20,221 --> 01:12:21,222
Robaire Junior?

1299
01:12:21,389 --> 01:12:22,891
She's been
taking care of him 24/7.

1300
01:12:23,016 --> 01:12:24,017
No.

1301
01:12:24,142 --> 01:12:25,185
And singing him lullabies
every night!

1302
01:12:25,352 --> 01:12:27,270
No, no, no, I haven't.

1303
01:12:27,437 --> 01:12:28,980
They're lying.

1304
01:12:29,064 --> 01:12:30,815
Here.

1305
01:12:30,899 --> 01:12:32,233
Found him at Tyler's.

1306
01:12:37,489 --> 01:12:39,157
4-Town forever?

1307
01:12:41,284 --> 01:12:43,119
4-Town forever.

1308
01:12:43,286 --> 01:12:45,580
- 4-Town forever.
- 4-Town forever!

1309
01:12:45,747 --> 01:12:47,582
Tyler?

1310
01:12:47,707 --> 01:12:50,877
No! Tyler? Who's Tyler?
I don't know a...

1311
01:12:51,044 --> 01:12:53,838
You are a 4-Townie?

1312
01:12:54,839 --> 01:12:55,840
No! Stop!

1313
01:12:56,007 --> 01:12:57,008
- No way!
- Yeah!

1314
01:12:57,133 --> 01:12:58,259
Welcome to the sisterhood!

1315
01:12:58,343 --> 01:12:59,511
Whatever, dorks.

1316
01:12:59,677 --> 01:13:00,804
Cut it out!

1317
01:13:00,970 --> 01:13:02,389
Your mom
must have gone nuclear.

1318
01:13:02,555 --> 01:13:04,265
Who cares?
What's she gonna do?

1319
01:13:04,349 --> 01:13:05,433
Ground me?

1320
01:13:09,229 --> 01:13:12,482
4-Town! 4-Town! 4-Town!

1321
01:13:12,649 --> 01:13:14,150
4-Town! 4-Town!

1322
01:13:19,406 --> 01:13:20,532
Let's go!

1323
01:13:20,615 --> 01:13:21,908
Is it starting? It's starting!

1324
01:13:22,075 --> 01:13:23,076
Guys, hold me.

1325
01:13:24,744 --> 01:13:28,331
Four, three, two, one!

1326
01:13:30,417 --> 01:13:32,544
<i>Are you ready?</i>

1327
01:13:35,463 --> 01:13:36,673
Oh, my gosh!

1328
01:13:37,549 --> 01:13:39,259
Yeah! Z!

1329
01:13:39,426 --> 01:13:40,635
I love you, man!

1330
01:13:41,344 --> 01:13:43,179
Yeah! Yeah!

1331
01:13:46,558 --> 01:13:48,143
Yes! Jesse!

1332
01:13:49,310 --> 01:13:52,647
<i>Toronto! Who knows what's up?</i>

1333
01:13:55,233 --> 01:13:56,609
Yes!

1334
01:14:00,363 --> 01:14:01,448
<i>You want it?</i>

1335
01:14:01,614 --> 01:14:02,615
<i>I want it</i>

1336
01:14:02,782 --> 01:14:04,784
<i>- You want it?
- I want it</i>

1337
01:14:05,076 --> 01:14:06,953
<i>- You want it?
- I want it</i>

1338
01:14:07,120 --> 01:14:09,456
<i>Give me one, two, three, four</i>

1339
01:14:10,039 --> 01:14:11,916
<i>You wanted it
You went for it</i>

1340
01:14:12,125 --> 01:14:13,168
<i>And, baby, you got it</i>

1341
01:14:14,377 --> 01:14:15,962
<i>I wanted it
I went for it</i>

1342
01:14:17,338 --> 01:14:21,718
<i>And, baby, I did it on my own</i>

1343
01:14:21,885 --> 01:14:26,848
<i>Did it on my own</i>

1344
01:14:27,640 --> 01:14:29,976
<i>Own</i>

1345
01:14:30,143 --> 01:14:31,144
<i>Did it on my own</i>

1346
01:14:31,227 --> 01:14:32,979
Mei-Mei!

1347
01:14:38,776 --> 01:14:39,777
No way!

1348
01:14:40,612 --> 01:14:41,905
Is this part of the show?

1349
01:14:44,240 --> 01:14:46,201
Is this special effects?

1350
01:14:46,784 --> 01:14:47,785
Help! Help!

1351
01:14:47,869 --> 01:14:50,121
Mei-Mei!

1352
01:14:50,663 --> 01:14:53,291
Where are you?

1353
01:14:55,084 --> 01:14:56,085
Mom?

1354
01:14:56,753 --> 01:14:57,754
Mei-Mei!

1355
01:15:04,886 --> 01:15:06,638
- I want a refund.
- What's her problem?

1356
01:15:06,804 --> 01:15:08,306
Mei!

1357
01:15:15,813 --> 01:15:17,106
It was just getting good!

1358
01:15:17,190 --> 01:15:18,358
This isn't cool.

1359
01:15:21,361 --> 01:15:23,279
- Mei! Mei!
- Dad?

1360
01:15:23,446 --> 01:15:24,656
We have to save your mother!

1361
01:15:24,822 --> 01:15:25,907
She's gone loco!

1362
01:15:26,074 --> 01:15:28,034
Mei, we have to do
the ritual again.

1363
01:15:28,201 --> 01:15:29,869
What happened? She's huge!

1364
01:15:30,036 --> 01:15:31,246
I told you she was big!

1365
01:15:31,454 --> 01:15:32,580
That big?

1366
01:15:32,789 --> 01:15:34,624
Mei-Mei!

1367
01:15:34,707 --> 01:15:35,875
Ming!
She's your daughter!

1368
01:15:36,042 --> 01:15:37,043
Mei!

1369
01:15:37,168 --> 01:15:38,336
- Let her go!
- Don't hurt her!

1370
01:15:38,503 --> 01:15:41,881
You are in big trouble,
young lady!

1371
01:15:42,048 --> 01:15:43,049
Mom! Let go!

1372
01:15:43,174 --> 01:15:45,218
I'm shutting this down,

1373
01:15:45,385 --> 01:15:47,053
right now!

1374
01:15:48,513 --> 01:15:50,473
Everyone, go home!

1375
01:15:50,640 --> 01:15:52,100
Where are your parents?

1376
01:15:52,267 --> 01:15:54,018
Put some clothes on!

1377
01:15:56,729 --> 01:15:59,607
This isn't you!

1378
01:16:00,733 --> 01:16:02,569
This is me!

1379
01:16:08,241 --> 01:16:09,909
- Mei-Mei!
- Mei! Are you hurt?

1380
01:16:11,286 --> 01:16:13,538
I'm not your little
Mei-Mei anymore!

1381
01:16:13,705 --> 01:16:15,665
I lied, Mom!

1382
01:16:15,832 --> 01:16:16,833
What?

1383
01:16:17,000 --> 01:16:19,377
It was my idea
to hustle the panda.

1384
01:16:19,544 --> 01:16:22,171
My idea
to go to Tyler's party!

1385
01:16:22,338 --> 01:16:24,507
It was all me!

1386
01:16:24,924 --> 01:16:26,134
I like boys!

1387
01:16:26,301 --> 01:16:28,094
I like loud music!

1388
01:16:28,261 --> 01:16:30,221
I like gyrating!

1389
01:16:30,388 --> 01:16:32,849
I'm 13! Deal with it!

1390
01:16:43,610 --> 01:16:46,195
The ritual.
Everyone in position.

1391
01:16:46,654 --> 01:16:48,239
Mei-Mei, keep her busy.

1392
01:16:48,406 --> 01:16:49,949
Oh, I'll keep her busy.

1393
01:16:50,700 --> 01:16:52,577
Where's Jin? Jin!

1394
01:16:53,828 --> 01:16:56,539
Mei!
Keep her in the circle!

1395
01:16:56,706 --> 01:16:58,625
Get back here!

1396
01:16:58,791 --> 01:17:00,126
Make me!

1397
01:17:00,293 --> 01:17:02,545
You think
you're so mature!

1398
01:17:03,129 --> 01:17:04,422
Lying to me!

1399
01:17:05,298 --> 01:17:06,924
Blaming me!

1400
01:17:07,091 --> 01:17:10,261
How could you be so, so...

1401
01:17:10,428 --> 01:17:12,138
crass?

1402
01:17:12,764 --> 01:17:15,016
Oh!
That's nothing!

1403
01:17:15,183 --> 01:17:16,934
You wanna see crass?

1404
01:17:18,561 --> 01:17:20,521
- What are you doing?
- You like that? Yes!

1405
01:17:20,688 --> 01:17:22,523
- Stop moving like that!
- What's wrong?

1406
01:17:22,690 --> 01:17:24,400
- Is this bothering you?
- Stop it!

1407
01:17:24,567 --> 01:17:25,735
Yeah, Mei!

1408
01:17:25,818 --> 01:17:27,695
Destroy her
with your big butt!

1409
01:17:27,987 --> 01:17:29,030
Yeah! Go, go, go!

1410
01:17:29,405 --> 01:17:31,199
Start singing now!

1411
01:17:31,366 --> 01:17:32,408
Ladies!

1412
01:17:35,370 --> 01:17:37,914
Stop!

1413
01:17:39,749 --> 01:17:40,792
Sing louder!

1414
01:17:40,958 --> 01:17:42,210
We're trying.

1415
01:17:43,044 --> 01:17:44,629
- Stop it!
- Let's get out of here!

1416
01:17:44,754 --> 01:17:46,005
Come on!

1417
01:17:46,130 --> 01:17:47,840
- Huh? Take it, Mom! Take it!
- No!

1418
01:17:49,425 --> 01:17:52,428
Stop it! Stop!

1419
01:17:58,810 --> 01:18:00,144
All I wanted...

1420
01:18:00,228 --> 01:18:04,023
...was to go to a concert!

1421
01:18:05,233 --> 01:18:07,652
I never went to concerts!

1422
01:18:07,819 --> 01:18:10,238
I put my family first!

1423
01:18:10,405 --> 01:18:12,699
I tried to be a good daughter!

1424
01:18:15,952 --> 01:18:17,912
Well, sorry I'm not perfect!

1425
01:18:18,121 --> 01:18:20,206
Sorry I'm not good enough!

1426
01:18:21,249 --> 01:18:24,168
And sorry
I'll never be like you!

1427
01:18:39,892 --> 01:18:40,893
Oh, no!

1428
01:18:41,060 --> 01:18:42,895
Mom... Mom!

1429
01:18:52,655 --> 01:18:53,781
No!

1430
01:18:57,368 --> 01:19:00,747
Mom!
You have to get in the circle!

1431
01:19:02,749 --> 01:19:04,041
Wake up!

1432
01:19:05,835 --> 01:19:07,086
I'm sorry!

1433
01:19:08,004 --> 01:19:09,922
Mom? Come on.

1434
01:19:10,757 --> 01:19:11,758
Please!

1435
01:19:18,848 --> 01:19:21,142
Sun Yee, give me strength.

1436
01:19:33,279 --> 01:19:34,947
- Pull, Mei-Mei!
- Grandma?

1437
01:19:35,114 --> 01:19:37,366
I am not losing my daughter.

1438
01:19:37,533 --> 01:19:38,826
Don't just stand there!

1439
01:19:55,885 --> 01:19:57,762
Make room
for your elders, Mei-Mei!

1440
01:19:57,845 --> 01:19:59,597
- What?
- We're with you!

1441
01:19:59,764 --> 01:20:01,432
But what are you doing?
What if you can't turn back?

1442
01:20:01,599 --> 01:20:03,351
- Your mom needs us!
- She's family!

1443
01:20:03,518 --> 01:20:05,311
Less talking, more pulling!

1444
01:20:05,478 --> 01:20:08,064
- This fur is so itchy!
- Quiet, Lily!

1445
01:20:20,034 --> 01:20:21,202
Louder!

1446
01:20:21,369 --> 01:20:22,995
Sing from the heart!

1447
01:20:23,162 --> 01:20:25,456
Louder!
The circle isn't working!

1448
01:20:35,925 --> 01:20:38,803
<i>- Never met nobody
- Nobody</i>

1449
01:20:40,346 --> 01:20:41,597
<i>Never met, never met,
never met</i>

1450
01:20:41,764 --> 01:20:45,893
<i>Like</i>

1451
01:20:46,269 --> 01:20:48,604
<i>You</i>

1452
01:20:57,446 --> 01:20:58,573
<i>Get up</i>

1453
01:20:58,739 --> 01:21:01,200
<i>I never met nobody</i>

1454
01:21:01,492 --> 01:21:02,869
<i>Like you</i>

1455
01:21:04,203 --> 01:21:05,872
<i>Had friends
and I've had buddies</i>

1456
01:21:06,163 --> 01:21:07,540
<i>It's true</i>

1457
01:21:07,623 --> 01:21:11,878
<i>But they don't turn my tummy
The way you do</i>

1458
01:21:12,211 --> 01:21:16,299
<i>I've never met nobody like you</i>

1459
01:21:17,049 --> 01:21:21,512
<i>You're never not on my mind
Oh, my, oh, my</i>

1460
01:21:21,679 --> 01:21:25,850
<i>I'm never not by your side
Your side, your side</i>

1461
01:21:26,058 --> 01:21:30,479
<i>I'm never gonna let you cry
Oh, cry, don't cry</i>

1462
01:21:30,730 --> 01:21:33,566
<i>I'll never not be
your ride or die</i>

1463
01:21:33,733 --> 01:21:37,153
<i>All right!</i>

1464
01:21:40,990 --> 01:21:42,450
Huh?

1465
01:21:43,951 --> 01:21:45,995
Mom? Mom!

1466
01:21:59,383 --> 01:22:02,428
Mom? Are you okay?
We have to...

1467
01:22:02,720 --> 01:22:05,181
Mom?

1468
01:22:05,681 --> 01:22:09,352
I'm sorry. It's all my fault.

1469
01:22:12,730 --> 01:22:13,898
What happened?

1470
01:22:14,982 --> 01:22:16,776
I... I hurt her.

1471
01:22:17,818 --> 01:22:18,819
Who?

1472
01:22:18,986 --> 01:22:20,112
My mom!

1473
01:22:20,696 --> 01:22:24,617
I got so angry,
and I lost control.

1474
01:22:26,035 --> 01:22:28,829
I'm just so sick
of being perfect!

1475
01:22:28,996 --> 01:22:31,290
I'm never gonna be
good enough for her.

1476
01:22:32,208 --> 01:22:33,501
Or anyone.

1477
01:22:46,847 --> 01:22:48,891
I know it feels that way.

1478
01:22:49,058 --> 01:22:51,310
Like, all the time.

1479
01:22:52,478 --> 01:22:56,816
But... it isn't true.

1480
01:23:02,321 --> 01:23:03,447
Come on.

1481
01:23:34,520 --> 01:23:35,646
Really? I could explode
at any moment.

1482
01:23:35,813 --> 01:23:37,023
- We have to find them.
- Where are they?

1483
01:23:37,189 --> 01:23:39,525
- Finally.
- Hurry, hurry!

1484
01:23:39,692 --> 01:23:40,776
Where have you been?
Come on!

1485
01:23:40,943 --> 01:23:43,112
- Let's get the lead out!
- Ladies.

1486
01:23:53,789 --> 01:23:56,459
- I'm sorry.
- Shh!

1487
01:23:56,751 --> 01:23:59,128
You don't have to apologize.

1488
01:24:01,547 --> 01:24:03,090
I'm your mother.

1489
01:24:08,679 --> 01:24:12,850
May Sun Yee guide you
and keep you safe.

1490
01:24:13,601 --> 01:24:16,437
One at a time, ladies.
And quickly.

1491
01:24:18,606 --> 01:24:19,607
That's it?

1492
01:24:19,774 --> 01:24:21,317
Mei-Mei's keeping the panda?

1493
01:24:21,484 --> 01:24:24,570
It's her life. Now move.

1494
01:24:47,760 --> 01:24:50,096
Go ahead. It's okay.

1495
01:25:12,326 --> 01:25:13,327
No.

1496
01:25:13,494 --> 01:25:17,039
Mei-Mei, please.
Just come with me.

1497
01:25:18,707 --> 01:25:21,252
I'm changing, Mom.

1498
01:25:21,919 --> 01:25:25,297
I'm finally figuring out
who I am.

1499
01:25:27,091 --> 01:25:29,593
But...

1500
01:25:29,802 --> 01:25:32,555
I'm scared it'll take me away
from you.

1501
01:25:35,224 --> 01:25:36,308
Me too.

1502
01:25:38,269 --> 01:25:39,937
I see you, Mei-Mei.

1503
01:25:40,688 --> 01:25:42,982
You try to make
everyone happy,

1504
01:25:43,065 --> 01:25:45,276
but are so hard on yourself.

1505
01:25:45,442 --> 01:25:48,154
And if I taught you that...

1506
01:25:50,573 --> 01:25:51,615
I'm sorry.

1507
01:25:53,576 --> 01:25:55,536
So, don't hold back.

1508
01:25:56,412 --> 01:25:57,496
For anyone.

1509
01:26:02,209 --> 01:26:03,961
The farther you go,

1510
01:26:04,753 --> 01:26:06,422
the prouder I'll be.

1511
01:26:24,815 --> 01:26:28,569
I'm not going
to regret this, am I?

1512
01:26:57,056 --> 01:27:00,726
<i>I'm Meilin Lee,
and ever since I turned 13,</i>

1513
01:27:00,893 --> 01:27:04,271
<i>life's been a lot.</i>

1514
01:27:04,438 --> 01:27:08,192
<i>People still talk about
Pandapocalypse 2002.</i>

1515
01:27:09,068 --> 01:27:11,153
<i>Mom and I just call it...</i>

1516
01:27:11,320 --> 01:27:12,446
<i>growing pains.</i>

1517
01:27:14,823 --> 01:27:17,243
This thing's hungry
all the time.

1518
01:27:17,409 --> 01:27:19,286
Eat up, little one.
Oh, you're so hungry.

1519
01:27:19,453 --> 01:27:21,038
- Munch, munch, munch.
- What?

1520
01:27:21,121 --> 01:27:23,415
Mr. Gao had to put
her panda in something.

1521
01:27:23,582 --> 01:27:25,084
You should see Grandma's.

1522
01:27:25,209 --> 01:27:28,712
Hmph! So unlucky.

1523
01:27:33,300 --> 01:27:34,301
You ready?

1524
01:27:34,468 --> 01:27:35,552
Let's do this.

1525
01:27:36,053 --> 01:27:38,264
- Hello! Welcome to our temple!
- What up, Toronto!

1526
01:27:38,430 --> 01:27:39,640
- Get in here!
- Yes, come on in.

1527
01:27:39,807 --> 01:27:42,184
And things at the temple
have never been better.

1528
01:27:42,351 --> 01:27:44,395
O-M-G! That looks so cute!

1529
01:27:44,561 --> 01:27:47,314
Our temple
is the oldest in Toronto.

1530
01:27:47,481 --> 01:27:51,360
And the only one that's home
to the great red panda.

1531
01:27:55,072 --> 01:27:56,156
Say "bamboo leaves!"

1532
01:27:56,323 --> 01:27:58,117
- Bamboo leaves!
- Mei!

1533
01:27:58,284 --> 01:27:59,576
- Hey!
- Guys!

1534
01:27:59,743 --> 01:28:01,036
- What's up?
- Bring it in!

1535
01:28:01,161 --> 01:28:02,997
Ready to get your karaoke on?

1536
01:28:03,163 --> 01:28:04,290
Totally.

1537
01:28:05,541 --> 01:28:06,750
Bye, Mom! Bye, Dad!

1538
01:28:06,917 --> 01:28:09,670
Hold on. You're not
going out like that, are you?

1539
01:28:09,837 --> 01:28:12,006
My panda,
my choice, Mom.

1540
01:28:12,923 --> 01:28:15,592
I'll be back
before dinner, okay?

1541
01:28:15,676 --> 01:28:17,845
